name: Mulvihill Enhanced Split Preferred Share ETF
longDescription: The Mulvihill Enhanced Split Preferred Share ETF offers tax-efficient monthly income while aiming to preserve capital through active management of a diversified portfolio primarily composed of preferred shares issued by Canadian split share corporations listed on a Canadian exchange. The ETF may employ leverage of up to 50% to enhance dividend income or pursue compelling investment opportunities, as deemed appropriate by the Manager.
